messages.message: Hey. I'm doing well. How have you been? Where are you working these days? Sorry about the slow response, but I rarely log on to Facebook.

Brian
Been good. On the job hunt. Working on a contract for a lady. Should be fun.
What kind of work you lookin for?

Brian
I guess they call it DevOps and full stack now. Hard to explain to recruiters because I wear so many different hats. Staffing is a huge waste of time.

My buddy recruits job seekers for companies. Take a look at his credentials (https://www.cybercoders.com/recruiter/brian-prather/) and let me know if you'd like me to connect the two of you.
Brian Prather - Executive Recruiter | CyberCoders
Are you looking for a new job or great hire? Meet Brian Prather, a CyberCoders recruiter who matches great people with great companies!
cybercoders.com

Brian
Yeah definitely. He looks great! I may have met someone from cybercoders. Insight global is a huge waste of time.

Brian
Got interviews in San Francisco with weebly and digit.co next week.
Very cool. Good luck with the interviews!
